  "title": "Facial Therapist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Highlights</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Friendly and comfortable working environment</li>\n  <li>Attractive salary and commission &amp; incentive plan</li>\n  <li>Employee discounts</li>\n  <li>Great opportunities for career development</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Warmly welcome customers and recommend appropriate care, treatment methods, and products based on their facial conditions.</li>\n  <li>Maintain a clean and hygienic environment.</li>\n  <li>Operate beauty treatment equipment skillfully and provide professional, high-quality skincare services.</li>\n  <li>Provide customers with knowledge and advice on beauty treatments, and patiently address their questions.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least two years of relevant work experience.</li>\n  <li>Possess relevant certificates and qualifications.</li>\n  <li>Maintain neat appearance and personal hygiene.</li>\n  <li>Polite, friendly, and possess good communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Have a basic understanding of TCM theory and skin-related knowledge.</li>\n  <li>Exhibit strong teamwork and collaboration skills.</li>\n</ul>",
